Gg_aim_ultimate

This map has 32 spawns, no Buy Zones, and is made for Gun Game.

-	32 Spawn points, 16 per team
-	Contains an overview radar
-	3d Skybox
-	Nav File for bots
-	No Buy Zones
-	Optimized with No Draw for better FPS
-	All files compiled into the .bsp using Pakrat
